ble, N., British bivalve seashells (1976) A Handbook for Identification, , Her Majesty's Stationary Office, London; Thieltges, D.W., Strasser, M., Van Beusekom, J.E.E., Reise, K., Too cold to prosper - Winter mortality prevents population increase of the introduced American slipper limpet Crepidula fornicata in northern Europe (2004) Journal of Experimental Marine Biology and Ecology, 311 (2), pp. 375-391. , DOI 10.1016/j.jembe.2004.05.018, PII S0022098104003247; Witt, M.J., Godley, B.J., A step towards seascape scale conservation: Using vessel monitoring systems (VMS) to map fishing activity (2007) PLoS ONE, 2, pp. e1111","Hinz, H.; School of Ocean Sciences, Bangor University, Menai Bridge, Anglesey LL59 5AB, United Kingdom; email: h.hinz@bangor.ac.uk",,,,,,,,01718630,,MESED,,"English","Mar. Ecol. Prog. Ser.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-79951638480
